text: Hamed Said Al-Khatri (born May 24, 1985) is an Omani sport shooter. He competed at the 2016 Summer Olympics in the men's 50 metre rifle three positions event, in which he placed 43rd. He was the flag bearer for Oman at the Parade of Nations. ==References== Category:1985 births Category:Living people Category:Omani male sport shooters Category:Olympic shooters of Oman Category:Shooters at the 2016 Summer Olympics Category:Shooters at the 2010 Asian Games Category:Shooters at the 2014 Asian Games Category:Shooters at the 2018 Asian Games Category:Asian Games competitors for Oman
